OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fbreaking through the evening, with
OL,7,Fsome late sunny spells. Partly cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight, with a chance of isolated
OL,9,Flight showers. Light winds continuing.
OL,10,FCold with a risk of frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA cold and rather bright
OL,13,Fstart. Becoming increasingly cloudy
OL,14,Fthrough the morning and afternoon,
OL,15,Fwith a chance of isolated showers
OL,16,Flater in the day. Winds remaining
OL,17,Flargely light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
